        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Mahit KC
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Web Developer with experience across front-end and back-end using JavaScript, PHP, MySQL,
          React, and WordPress. Built database-driven web apps, optimized legacy PHP services, and
          improved UI consistency in Agile teams. Strong foundation in Linux/Windows administration,
          security best practices, and collaborative development.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-10">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#6B72FF]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-4.243-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
            Bedford, Nova Scotia
